			<tr><td colspan="2">
				<div class="postbody">
				Is it the end of small business/entrepreneurship or does it provide new opportunities for small business?
<br />

<br />
I won't lie, I'm not a big fan of Wal-Mart but you can't compete with pricing that's discounted so much based on large quantity sales and lowered wholesale purchasing prices.  
<br />

<br />
I have my thoughts on what will happen in the next 2-5 years but I'm wondering more what you folks think about this.  We were discussing it in my International Marketing class last week and the majority of the class felt that Wal-Mart will literally destroy "corner shop stores".
<br />

<br />
Discuss!
<br />

<br />

<br />
-Imirik<br />
				<span class="gensmall"></span><br />
				</div>
			</td></tr>
